OL,3,GSouth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FUnsettled, with frequent
OL,6,Fshowers and bands of rain pushing
OL,7,Feastwards throughout the day. Windy,
OL,8,Fespecially around the coasts where
OL,9,Fgales are likely. Turning drier and
OL,10,Fbrighter across Cornwall later in the
OL,11,Fafternoon. Feeling rather cool.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FHeavy showers will clear
OL,14,Feastwards during the evening. Mostly
OL,15,Fdry overnight, with clear spells.
OL,16,FHowever, a few light showers remain
OL,17,Fpossible. Staying breezy.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
