OL,3,GSouth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CSunday:FA mostly dry day, with spells
OL,6,Fof sunshine. An increasing risk of
OL,7,Fshowery outbreaks of rain developing
OL,8,Flate afternoon, turning heavy over the
OL,9,Fhills by the evening. Breezy.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:
OL,12,FStaying unsettled, with a mixture of
OL,13,Fsunny spells and showery rain. Some of
OL,14,Fthe showers could be heavy and
OL,15,Fthundery. Temperatures a little below
OL,16,Fnormal, with some chilly nights.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
